cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically the estimation of material and illumination from photographs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization procedures and neural networks, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of multiple images to estimate material and illumination, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
